<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
      /* Styling umum */
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        color: #333;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 50px;
    }
    
    /* Container untuk halaman error */
    .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    /* Judul halaman */
    h1 {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #dc3545;
    }
    
    /* Pesan error */
    p {
        font-size: 13px;
        margin: 10px 0 20px;
    }
    
    /* Tombol kembali */
    .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        font-size: 16px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
        background-color: #007bff;
        border-radius: 5px;
        transition: 0.3s;
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
        background-color: #0056b3;
    }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h1><%= title %> - Halaman Tidak Ditemukan</h1>
        <p>Maaf, halaman yang Anda cari tidak tersedia.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Kembali ke Beranda</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
